Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.42,0:22:11.80,ED03 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13\fad(498,258)}Even if we part and meet again, I want to meet at this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.89,0:22:18.73,ED03 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13\fad(258,498)}Then we'll hold hands to ensure we'll never be separated again.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.81,0:22:21.36,ED03 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13\i1}We used to talk all night until the sun rose,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.36,0:22:24.19,ED03 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13\i1}And held hands till the sun went under the horizon.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.19,0:22:29.45,ED03 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13\fad(0,258)\i1}Let's walk together like this forever, like light and shadow.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.53,0:22:33.99,ED03 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13\fad(258,0)}I stand in the city, staring off into space with lonely eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.99,0:22:39.33,ED03 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}I can't find warmth on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.33,0:22:44.84,ED03 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13\fad(0,258)}By meeting you, I realized
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.00,0:22:50.68,ED03 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13\fad(258,0)}How much strength love could give me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.68,0:22:55.93,ED03 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}Even if we part and meet again, I want to meet at this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.93,0:23:01.23,ED03 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}Then we'll hold hands to ensure we'll never be separated again.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.23,0:23:06.44,ED03 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}I can't sleep by myself, 'cause I can't dream without you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.44,0:23:12.20,ED03 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}So take me to a place where uncertainty can't reach us
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.20,0:23:17.45,ED03 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13\fad(0,498)}And let us bring light to the night sky with no stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.70,0:23:19.96,ED03 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13\i1}So long as you're with me, I can go to world's end.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.96,0:23:22.96,ED03 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13\i1}Even if it's a path I can't walk on my own,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.96,0:23:26.00,ED03 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13\i1}If you're by my side, I can walk it while humming a tune.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.00,0:23:29.42,ED03 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13\fad(0,498)\i1}If we're together, the world is mine.{\i0}
