Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.80,0:01:58.97,Default,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Where could she be?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.86,0:02:15.23,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,East City!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.23,0:02:16.90,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,You've arrived in East City!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.49,0:02:27.29,Default,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,Here's the latest news on Scar.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.29,0:02:29.08,Default,Sol2,0000,0000,0000,,He's still on the run?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.25,0:02:31.21,Default,Sol2,0000,0000,0000,,What a persistent guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.09,0:02:36.96,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my, I'm terribly sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.96,0:02:39.68,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's my fault for not paying attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.09,0:02:43.26,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,You are wearing some unusual attire.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.68,0:02:45.22,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Are you not from this country?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.64,0:02:47.14,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,I'm from Xing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.14,0:02:48.39,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.39,0:02:49.48,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Are you here to see the sights?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.02,0:02:53.06,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,There's not much to see in East City, is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.06,0:02:56.19,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,No, I just stopped by because I need to switch trains here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.03,0:02:58.94,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,I'm headed to the North.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.94,0:03:02.82,Default-alt,Man,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}The train at Platform No. 3 is headed for North City.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.70,0:03:01.61,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.82,0:03:04.53,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for helping me pick up the groceries!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.32,0:03:06.24,Default-alt,Man,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}If you are planning on riding with us, please board at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.08,0:03:06.24,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Have a safe trip!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.29,0:03:11.87,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.38,0:03:18.88,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,What a peculiar kitty.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.36,0:03:42.61,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Where did he go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.61,0:03:45.20,Default,Man2,0000,0000,0000,,I know I heard footsteps...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.91,0:03:51.00,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,There he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.18,0:04:10.81,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,So he was with a middle-aged man with black hair?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.81,0:04:13.48,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. According to the reports, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.44,0:04:21.03,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,This is where he was yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.99,0:04:27.28,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,So he's headed West, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.74,0:04:30.58,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,We have a few injured, some slightly, others seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.79,0:04:33.79,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Scar must be desperate, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.46,0:04:36.17,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,But even so...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.38,0:04:39.17,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,...he's attracting a lot of attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.38,0:04:47.59,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let's head off to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.25,0:05:16.87,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Well, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.87,0:05:18.79,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,That has nothing to do with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.19,0:05:40.81,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,A funeral, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.15,0:05:44.32,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it seems so.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.90,0:05:46.95,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,It isn't pretty, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.95,0:05:52.87,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,When you get old like me, you can't help but think about when you'll be the one getting buried.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.37,0:05:55.83,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,What a terrible thing to say, madam.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.83,0:05:57.58,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,As far as I can see, you have a long life ahead of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.67,0:06:07.30,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Lieutenant General Grumman?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.18,0:06:13.18,Default,Grum,0000,0000,0000,,You said we were going to meet in front of Brigadier General Hughes' grave, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.06,0:06:19.94,Default,Grum,0000,0000,0000,,I figured it was something serious since you decided to take the measure of last resort.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.94,0:06:23.57,Default,Grum,0000,0000,0000,,To be doubly sure, I decided to disguise myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.57,0:06:27.36,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I shouldn't have expected less from you, a man so famous for his eccentricity.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.36,0:06:28.90,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Your disguise exceeded my expectations.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.36,0:06:30.49,Default,Grum,0000,0000,0000,,Eccentric?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.03,0:06:33.99,Default,Grum,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take that as a compliment.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.66,0:06:36.91,Default,Grum,0000,0000,0000,,So, what's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.37,0:06:39.92,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Eastern Alchemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.21,0:06:43.46,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,We may be able to find something in the Central Library.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.46,0:06:44.67,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.67,0:06:49.59,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Since we can't find the midget,\Nwe'll have to search on our own.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.59,0:06:52.43,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,I hope we can at least find some clues.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.43,0:06:58.68,Default,Grum,0000,0000,0000,,I see. So the entire upper echelon of Central is guilty, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.60,0:07:03.69,Default,Grum,0000,0000,0000,,But you lost far too much in exchange for the information.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.23,0:07:08.69,Default,Grum,0000,0000,0000,,You have nothing left if they take away the men you can trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.19,0:07:11.78,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,You're right, sir. I can't argue with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.45,0:07:15.53,Default,Grum,0000,0000,0000,,Even Raven, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.58,0:07:23.08,Default,Grum,0000,0000,0000,,When I was in Central a little while ago, Raven asked me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.67,0:07:28.46,Default,Grum,0000,0000,0000,,"Are you interested in a perfect, immortal army?"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.13,0:07:30.47,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Immortal army?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.63,0:07:34.39,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Was he talking about the Homunculi?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.55,0:07:38.47,Default,Grum,0000,0000,0000,,I flat-out rejected him, saying that it was rubbish.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.81,0:07:41.14,Default,Grum,0000,0000,0000,,Then soon after,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.06,0:07:44.56,Default,Grum,0000,0000,0000,,I was sent to Eastern Headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.81,0:07:46.57,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Relegated?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.27,0:07:52.99,Default,Grum,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to that, I'm now stuck cleaning up after all the messes in the East.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.11,0:07:58.45,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,More on that topic, do you happen to remember the riot in Lior?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.95,0:08:05.33,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,The case where the Fullmetal Alchemist exposed the fake priest of Leto's conspiracy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.96,0:08:07.96,Default,Grum,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I do remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.63,0:08:13.30,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Although Lior was thrown into disarray,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.30,0:08:19.51,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,the riot was quickly suppressed thanks to the\NEastern Army's rapid response while it was still minor.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.10,0:08:26.10,Default,Grum,0000,0000,0000,,But the Central Army intruded on the scene, and the Eastern Army was withdrawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.65,0:08:28.02,Default,Grum,0000,0000,0000,,Am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.69,0:08:29.23,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.98,0:08:36.82,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Lior's public order suddenly turned for\Nthe worse when the Central Army entered the scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.74,0:08:41.91,Default,Grum,0000,0000,0000,,Those guys at Central are really\Nplanning something, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.29,0:08:45.29,Default,Grum,0000,0000,0000,,I don't even want to think about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.29,0:08:47.92,Default,Grum,0000,0000,0000,,Can't things be peaceful until I retire?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.42,0:08:50.17,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Again with the jokes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.96,0:08:53.34,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,You're the great Lieutenant General Grumman.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.88,0:08:57.59,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you haven't felt satisfied for a second at simply being the head man for a region of the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.43,0:09:04.06,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,You have the Eastern Army on your side;\Nfull of veteran soldiers who experienced Ishbal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.15,0:09:14.82,Default,Grum,0000,0000,0000,,I had always thought you'd use that secret contact memo when you needed to whine and beg me for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.03,0:09:18.57,Default,Grum,0000,0000,0000,,But you called me here to get me worked up, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.28,0:09:20.66,Default,Grum,0000,0000,0000,,Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.16,0:09:24.87,Default,Grum,0000,0000,0000,,Now that things are getting interesting in Central,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.87,0:09:30.34,Default,Grum,0000,0000,0000,,the flame of ambition in my heart has been lit once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.13,0:09:34.34,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get too serious or your makeup will be ruined, madam.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.51,0:09:35.92,Default,Grum,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.18,0:09:40.97,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Are you free after this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.43,0:09:43.81,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't mind, would you like to join me for a cup of tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.81,0:09:45.85,Default,Grum,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.85,0:09:47.98,Default,Grum,0000,0000,0000,,I appreciate the invitation, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.99,0:10:02.99,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,It's no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.12,0:10:07.54,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Why doesn't this place have any good books on Eastern Alchemy?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.71,0:10:12.34,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I'll just visit Xing and study there instead...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.21,0:10:17.17,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, but there's no way I'll be able to cross that desert with my automail...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.64,0:10:31.73,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,There you are, Edward Elric.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.86,0:10:35.32,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,M-Major! What are you doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.32,0:10:36.03,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,Shh!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.03,0:10:38.57,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,You have to be quiet in the library.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.78,0:10:45.79,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,I heard you're after a girl from Xing\Nwho carries around a black and white cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.79,0:10:46.95,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.95,0:10:48.54,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, how did you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.33,0:10:51.50,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,I heard from Colonel Mustang.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.50,0:10:54.29,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here today on the Colonel's orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.17,0:10:57.92,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, she's headed north.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.72,0:11:03.80,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,According to a witness, she was in\NEast City and was headed north from there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.72,0:11:06.06,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,North, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.06,0:11:08.18,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. If we know that much, it's safe to give it a try.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.73,0:11:10.27,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks a lot, Major.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.77,0:11:12.31,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Tell the Colonel I said thanks, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.31,0:11:13.44,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,Hang on.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.44,0:11:14.44,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be in such a rush.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.48,0:11:18.44,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,Take this with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.07,0:11:21.11,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.49,0:11:22.91,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,It's a letter of introduction.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.41,0:11:25.37,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,It may not do you much good,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.24,0:11:27.37,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,but you should meet her first.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.20,0:11:30.50,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Meet who?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.17,0:11:34.83,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,She resides even farther north than the Northern Headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.63,0:11:40.55,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,A general who guards the Drakma border and holds another name, the "Northern Wall of Briggs"...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.59,0:11:44.84,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,...Major General Armstrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.07,0:12:03.91,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.82,0:12:07.95,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,You've got nowhere to run, Scar!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.94,0:12:35.65,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Where did he go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.53,0:12:42.03,Default,Man2,0000,0000,0000,,Report this to Headquarters!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.49,0:12:44.28,Default,Man2,0000,0000,0000,,That train is headed for West City!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.86,0:12:45.99,Default,Man2,0000,0000,0000,,Damn him...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.28,0:12:52.83,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,I can't really find much on Eastern Alchemy...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.04,0:12:57.96,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,May's long-distance transmutation was awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.84,0:13:01.21,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I could use that...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.21,0:13:05.18,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,I should have asked her about it when she was still at Dr. Nox's place.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.63,0:13:10.18,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Ling said that it's used predominantly for medical purposes...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.10,0:13:20.23,Default,Selim,0000,0000,0000,,Are you the Fullmetal Alchemist's little brother who wears a giant suit wherever he goes?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.65,0:13:22.48,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.48,0:13:24.11,Default,Selim,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.11,0:13:26.11,Default,Selim,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.95,0:13:28.11,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.11,0:13:30.66,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,But you need to keep it down. We're in a library.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.66,0:13:32.12,Default,Selim,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.29,0:13:35.25,Default,Selim,0000,0000,0000,,What are you studying?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.66,0:13:37.21,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Eastern Alchemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.67,0:13:39.21,Default,Selim,0000,0000,0000,,Eastern Alchemy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.21,0:13:41.38,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,It's a form of alchemy used in Xing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.92,0:13:44.26,Default,Selim,0000,0000,0000,,Wow... Xing, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.09,0:13:53.81,Default,Selim,0000,0000,0000,,But aren't you Elric Brothers skilled enough to be state qualified in Amestris, a nation so advanced in alchemy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.35,0:13:58.77,Default,Selim,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you researching minor forms of alchemy used in other countries?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.77,0:13:59.31,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.27,0:14:07.90,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,I can't exactly say, "I'm looking for a way to get my body back and fight Homunculi"...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.91,0:14:09.70,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.41,0:14:14.70,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,They say that Eastern Alchemy is used predominantly for medical purposes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.70,0:14:20.50,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,I'm researching to see if there are any other ways human lives could be saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.50,0:14:23.80,Default,Selim,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! Nothing less to be expected from the Elric Brothers!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.09,0:14:26.34,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Al! Alphonse!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.34,0:14:27.72,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Get your things together! We're leaving!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.38,0:14:30.89,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Brother, you have to keep it down in the library!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.51,0:14:33.22,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, where are we going?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.56,0:14:36.18,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I'll explain the details on the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.18,0:14:37.60,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Either way, we need to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.60,0:14:39.39,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Go to the hotel and pack.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.31,0:14:41.35,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Whose brat is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.69,0:14:48.19,Default,Selim,0000,0000,0000,,If you're his brother, it must mean you're Edward, the State Alchemist!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.19,0:14:48.74,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.90,0:14:50.03,Default,Selim,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.03,0:14:52.49,Default,Selim,0000,0000,0000,,So the rumors were true! You really are a tiny alchemist!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.07,0:14:54.62,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.04,0:14:58.04,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.04,0:14:59.79,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Say that again...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.79,0:15:01.54,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, say it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.54,0:15:02.71,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,You're up for a ride.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.71,0:15:05.04,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Want me to blast you to Neptune?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.21,0:15:06.21,Default,Selim,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.21,0:15:09.13,Default,Selim,0000,0000,0000,,So they were right! You get really angry when people say you're short!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.09,0:15:13.89,Default,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Back away from Sir Selim!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.60,0:15:16.10,Default,Selim,0000,0000,0000,,You can't shoot him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.10,0:15:20.10,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me... you're Selim Bradley?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.73,0:15:22.35,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,The Führer President's son?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.35,0:15:24.98,Default,Selim,0000,0000,0000,,Yup! That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.70,0:15:34.78,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck are we doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.78,0:15:37.04,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't we supposed to be headed north?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.04,0:15:39.20,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Not like it was my choice...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.20,0:15:40.96,Default,Wife,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.66,0:15:44.58,Default,Wife,0000,0000,0000,,This boy has admired you for so long, Mr. Edward.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.38,0:15:46.71,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Admired?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.71,0:15:49.92,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Do you like alchemy, Selim?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.92,0:15:50.84,Default,Selim,0000,0000,0000,,I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.84,0:15:56.80,Default,Selim,0000,0000,0000,,My dream is to learn alchemy and become a State Alchemist like Mr. Edward.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.80,0:15:58.47,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Admired me, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.35,0:15:58.47,Default-alt,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.64,0:16:01.35,Default,Selim,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I want to be useful to Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.73,0:16:07.11,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Do you love your Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.44,0:16:11.36,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,...Führer President King Bradley?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.53,0:16:12.74,Default,Selim,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.95,0:16:16.37,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,What's he like?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.37,0:16:18.12,Default,Selim,0000,0000,0000,,He's a very noble man.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.12,0:16:21.75,Default,Selim,0000,0000,0000,,He perseveres through hard work that would make a normal person cry...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.75,0:16:25.25,Default,Selim,0000,0000,0000,,...and works every day with only one thing in mind: the well-being of his people.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.08,0:16:27.79,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.79,0:16:31.01,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,The Führer President {\i1}does{\i0\fscx20} {\r} seem busy all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.67,0:16:34.43,Default,Wife,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.88,0:16:38.93,Default,Wife,0000,0000,0000,,He still plans on working to his fullest in active service.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.56,0:16:42.93,Default,Wife,0000,0000,0000,,I'm constantly telling him to retire already, bearing his age in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.60,0:16:47.06,Default,Wife,0000,0000,0000,,He's always been someone totally committed to his work.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.73,0:16:53.44,Default,Wife,0000,0000,0000,,He can do his job, but he's always been a blockhead when it comes to women.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.70,0:16:58.07,Default,Wife,0000,0000,0000,,He was so impolite; I gave him a good slap across the face.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.83,0:17:01.83,Default,Wife,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's where it all started. Then, we started dating.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.83,0:17:03.96,Default,Wife,0000,0000,0000,,And our first date was...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.96,0:17:05.83,Default,Wife,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.83,0:17:08.29,Default,Wife,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't mean to talk about senseless things.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.26,0:17:20.51,Default,Selim,0000,0000,0000,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.51,0:17:21.22,Default,Wife,0000,0000,0000,,What a surprise!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.68,0:17:24.06,Default,Selim,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.06,0:17:25.98,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Selim.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.77,0:17:28.10,Default,Wife,0000,0000,0000,,Why the surprise visit?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.77,0:17:33.03,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,I had some rare free time, so I came to see your faces.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.32,0:17:38.61,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I heard the Fullmetal Alchemist was here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.87,0:17:39.78,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.78,0:17:41.20,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.62,0:17:44.95,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,We just saw each other at Central Headquarters, didn't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.13,0:17:54.84,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,I see. So you met each other at the library.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.13,0:17:56.01,Default,Selim,0000,0000,0000,,Yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.14,0:18:03.22,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,What, are you trying to say that we don't look alike?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.51,0:18:05.98,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, that's not it...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.18,0:18:08.73,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,We're not connected by blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.31,0:18:12.27,Default,Wife,0000,0000,0000,,We were never able to have kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.07,0:18:15.74,Default,Wife,0000,0000,0000,,So we adopted him from a relative.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.45,0:18:20.91,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,He grew up to become a kind boy who cares so much for his parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.91,0:18:22.49,Default,Selim,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.66,0:18:24.29,Default,Selim,0000,0000,0000,,It's embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.29,0:18:26.20,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,I'm only stating the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.25,0:18:34.17,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,Is something the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.13,0:18:41.76,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, it's just that we only see you when you're working at Headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.76,0:18:43.89,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,So it's just... right, Brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.89,0:18:46.52,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I guess we're just stunned to see such a different side of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.10,0:18:48.39,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.98,0:18:51.60,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,I, too, have family.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.60,0:18:53.40,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,Even someone like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.27,0:18:58.15,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,Although it's a bit different from your family.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.12,0:19:12.83,Default,Selim,0000,0000,0000,,Are you leaving already, Father?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.83,0:19:16.59,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. It's about time for me to return to the office.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.68,0:19:23.97,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,Enjoy your stay,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.39,0:19:26.47,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,State Alchemist.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.06,0:19:35.98,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.45,0:19:49.79,Default,Selim,0000,0000,0000,,Come visit again!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.79,0:19:52.04,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.92,0:20:05.93,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think his wife or son know that he's a Homunculus...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.14,0:20:14.90,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, we need to head north! All the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.23,0:20:20.11,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,We need to get a hold of that midget and\Nmake her tell us the secret behind Eastern Alchemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.11,0:20:20.90,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.62,0:20:29.04,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be there by morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.04,0:20:30.16,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,Sleep for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.60,0:20:52.64,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,I see... so you let them get away again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.73,0:20:59.02,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,This is a map of the West, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.19,0:21:00.40,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.69,0:21:06.11,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,He was last seen...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.32,0:21:07.20,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.32,0:21:10.28,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,And this is West City.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.29,0:21:15.50,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Scar and Marcoh disappeared somewhere in between.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.96,0:21:22.76,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,A train must slow down significantly at a curve, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.80,0:21:26.18,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Is it possible for someone to jump off?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.55,0:21:29.39,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't say it's impossible, but it's very dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.30,0:21:31.47,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.85,0:21:37.40,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, I wonder which direction they ran after they jumped off?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.10,0:21:39.36,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,North...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.44,0:21:41.57,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,...or south...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.64,0:23:38.35,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be our first time traveling north?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.35,0:23:39.39,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.85,0:23:42.35,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if we'll be able to see snow?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.35,0:23:43.77,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Snow, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.52,0:23:48.15,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it rarely stuck to the ground in Resembool.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.58,0:24:01.29,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,The cat and the mouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.29,0:24:04.54,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Insanity and hatred clash in a white world.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.50,0:24:10.21,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,The fiercest battle yet opens the gate to a new world.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.59,0:24:15.76,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, Fullmetal Alchemist:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.76,0:24:19.89,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 33, The Northern Wall of Briggs.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.81,0:24:25.48,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Her golden hair is a flame made of ice.
